    <section ids="ec-init init" names="ec\ init init">
        <title>EC Init</title>
        <paragraph>EC Initialization code takes the embedded controller from the reset state to a state where the RTOS can run.
            It usually configures the basic registers and initializes some devices.
            Initial hardware configuration involves setting up the target platform so it can work as required and communicate with system.</paragraph>
